(272, 20, 28, 'Larry Thomas is a 39-year veteran real estate Principal Broker who has personally  sold over 2,353 homes during his career. He has also built and owned three independent real estate companies over that same period of time. In his position of Owner/Broker, he was responsible to review, oversee,and repair when necessary, the closing of thousands of real estate transactions written by agents under his supervision. He has also been a Divisional Vice President for American Express and trained hundreds of salespeople in financial planning, stock brokerage, insurance, real estate and investing.\r\n\r\nOver the past 39-years, Larry has purchased, remodeled, and resold investment homes for fun and profit. He has a master\\''s vision on improving real estate, he understands cost effective repairs and knows how to earn profits in commercial and residential housing. He is also able to combine the worlds of financial planning, investing, IRAs and other tax avoidance vehicles to maximize the real profits to any real estate investor.\r\n\r\nIn 2008 he sold his 124-agent company, the twelfth largest real estate company in Portland, OR in order to retire to Vancouver, WA. After a few months of retirement he found himself bored with little to do. Since real estate values were falling through out the country and home sales were down, Larry looked for a niche market where demand was still strong. He found it in the For Sale by Owner and Expired Listing arenas, where many sellers found their equity had declined and needed to reduce their selling costs in order to sell their homes profitably.\r\n\r\nAlacarte Solutions Inc, has been designed to help For-Sale-by-Owners sell their own home in order to maximize their profits. Larry and his Realtor wife, Marillyn, encourage sellers to perform the real estate marketing tasks they feel comfortable doing and use a licensed Real Estate Broker for efforts they don\\''t want to do or don\\''t have the time to do. When marketing homes this way it has been proven that sellers can sell faster, keep more of their equity, save the real estate commission and put more money into their own pocket at closing.\r\n\r\n If you have questions about our systems feel free to call us at 360-433-2437 or email us at alacarterealestate@comcast.net.', '2013-09-05 20:06:00'),
