(179, 1, '2013-08-19 04:18:26', '2013-08-19 04:18:26', 'Privacy Policy. Choose My Rep\r\nProtecting your private information is our priority.\r\n\r\nThis Statement of Privacy applies to the www.ChooseMyRep.com and Choose My Rep LLC and governs data collection and usage. For the purposes of this Privacy Policy, unless otherwise noted, all references to Choose My Rep LLC include www.ChooseMyRep.com and Choose My Rep. The Choose My Rep website is a Social Website site. By using the Choose My Rep website, you consent to the data practices described in this statement.\r\n\r\nCollection of your Personal Information\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep may collect personally identifiable information, such as your name. If you purchase Choose My Rep''s products and services, we collect billing and credit card information. This information is used to complete the purchase transaction. Choose My Rep may also collect anonymous demographic information, which is not unique to you, such as your age and gender. We may gather additional personal or non-personal information in the future. Information about your computer hardware and software may be automatically collected by Choose My Rep. This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times and referring website addresses. This information is used for the operation of the service, to maintain quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the Choose My Rep website.\r\n\r\nPlease keep in mind that if you directly disclose personally identifiable information or personally sensitive data through Choose My Rep''s public message boards, this information may be collected and used by others.\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep encourages you to review the privacy statements of websites you choose to link to from Choose My Rep so that you can understand how those websites collect, use and share your information. Choose My Rep is not responsible for the privacy statements or other content on websites outside of the Choose My Rep website.\r\n\r\nUse of your Personal Information\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep collects and uses your personal information to operate its website(s) and deliver the services you have requested.\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep may also use your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from Choose My Rep and its affiliates. Choose My Rep may also contact you via surveys to conduct research about your opinion of current services or of potential new services that may be offered.\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep does not sell, rent or lease its customer lists to third parties. Choose My Rep may share data with trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to Choose My Rep, and they are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information.\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep may keep track of the websites and pages our users visit within Choose My Rep, in order to determine what Choose My Rep services are the most popular. This data is used to deliver customized content and advertising within Choose My Rep to customers whose behavior indicates that they are interested in a particular subject area.\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep will disclose your personal information, without notice, only if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on Choose My Rep or the site; (b) protect and defend the rights or property of Choose My Rep; and, (c) act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of Choose My Rep, or the public.\r\n\r\nUse of Cookies\r\n\r\nThe Choose My Rep website may use "cookies" to help you personalize your online experience. A cookie is a text file that is placed on your hard disk by a web page server. Cookies cannot be used to run programs or deliver viruses to your computer. Cookies are uniquely assigned to you, and can only be read by a web server in the domain that issued the cookie to you.\r\n\r\nOne of the primary purposes of cookies is to provide a convenience feature to save you time. The purpose of a cookie is to tell the Web server that you have returned to a specific page. For example, if you personalize Choose My Rep pages, or register with Choose My Rep site or services, a cookie helps Choose My Rep to recall your specific information on subsequent visits. This simplifies the process of recording your personal information, such as billing addresses, shipping addresses, and so on. When you return to the same Choose My Rep website, the information you previously provided can be retrieved, so you can easily use the Choose My Rep features that you customized. You have the ability to accept or decline cookies. Most Web browsers automatically accept cookies, but you can usually modify your browser setting to decline cookies if you prefer. If you choose to decline cookies, you may not be able to fully experience the interactive features of the Choose My Rep services or websites you visit.\r\n\r\nSecurity of your Personal Information\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep secures your personal information from unauthorized access, use or disclosure. When personal information (such as a credit card number) is transmitted to other websites, it is protected through the use of encryption, such as the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) protocol.\r\n\r\nChildren Under Thirteen\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of thirteen. If you are under the age of thirteen, you must ask your parent or guardian for permission to use this website.\r\n\r\nOpt-Out &amp; Unsubscribe\r\n\r\nWe respect your privacy and give you an opportunity to opt-out of receiving announcements of certain information. Users may opt-out of receiving any or all communications from Choose My Rep by contacting us.\r\n\r\nChanges to this Statement\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep will occasionally update this Statement of Privacy to reflect company and customer feedback. Choose My Rep encourages you to periodically review this Statement to be informed of how Choose My Rep is protecting your information.\r\n\r\nContact Information\r\n\r\nChoose My Rep, LLC\r\n\r\n10117 SE Sunnyside RD STE F #730\r\n\r\nClackamas, OR 97015', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2013-08-19 04:18:26', '2013-08-19 04:18:26', '', 0, 'http://dev.choosemyrep.com/?page_id=179', 0, 'page', '', 0),
